{
  "stem": "19923.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've been told between that I used the word [NON-ENGLISH], which means strength, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you also enquired, how could we keep the chicken?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we had a metal basin about, I would say, 2, 2 and 1/2 feet in length, and the handles came lower.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father would put the chicken in the basin and turn the basin upside down and shove it underneath our bed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This allowed air to come through, but it certainly didn't prevent the chicken from clucking and hitting the sides of the basin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sometimes we'd have a few sleepless nights with all the noise that was being made by the chicken.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that's the way we kept the chicken, until my father had a chance to take him to the [NON-ENGLISH] to have him slaughtered or killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, getting back to my early childhood, I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For some reason, I had nightmares, horrible nightmares, and they were always the same, of me falling.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were shapes and sounds, but nothing-- nothing that I could put in-- into any living description.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just feelings and sounds and shapes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as a result of that, I was-- I was ill a lot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had every imaginable illness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was decided that I should be singled out to go to camp during the summer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So for about two or three years, the Jewish community allowed me to go to a summer camp in Kreuznach, which is in Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's a very-- what we would call now a resort area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if you want me to spell it out--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's K-R-E-U-T-Z-N-A-C-H.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I visited that place when I was an adult, and I went back and I reminisced.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had some fond memories of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
